# Steps to install SASS

1. Navigated to my project repository:
   $ cd ~/Documents/alx-intermediate-frontend

2. Created a new directory for the task:
   $ mkdir 0x03-sass_scss
   $ cd 0x03-sass_scss

3. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using npm:
   $ npm install sass@3.7.4

4. Verified the installation:
   $ npx sass --version
